("3818","en","default","2bc6f983917576292a23bcbf9c5ecf74","The Text mode allows you to enter HTML along with your post text. Note that &lt;p&gt; and &lt;br&gt; tags are converted to line breaks when switching to the Text editor to make it less cluttered. When you type, a single line break can be used instead of typing &lt;br&gt;, and two line breaks instead of paragraph tags. The line breaks are converted back to tags automatically.","0","LINE","","0","","6822422cfd888b5560ab16ce486fcf0f"),
