("687","1","2018-09-18 00:28:42","2018-09-17 17:28:42","[ux_banner height=\"198px\" bg=\"269\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.31)\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"40\" width__sm=\"60\" position_x=\"0\" position_y=\"50\" text_align=\"left\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">General Introduction</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/?lang=en\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"/about-us/?lang=en\">About us</a> &gt; General Introduction</p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[section label=\"Section gioi thieu\" class=\"section-gioi-thieu\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\" class=\"cot1\"]\n\n[title text=\"ABOUT MOBIPLUS\"]\n\n<div class=\"menu-gioi-thieu-chung\">\n<p><a href=\"/general-introduction/?lang=en\">General introduction</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/our-partners/?lang=en\">Our Partners</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/customer/?lang=en\">Our Customer</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/social-activities/?lang=en\">Social Activities</a></p>\n</div>\n[gap height=\"20px\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tieu-de\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600; font-size: 95%;\">NEWS - RECRUITMENT<br />\n</span></h3>\n[blog_posts style=\"vertical\" type=\"row\" col_spacing=\"small\" columns=\"1\" columns__md=\"1\" cat=\"3\" posts=\"5\" show_date=\"false\" excerpt=\"false\" comments=\"false\" image_height=\"89%\" image_width=\"25\" text_pos=\"middle\" text_align=\"left\" text_size=\"small\"]\n\n[contact-form-7 id=\"799\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>Mobi Plus is a provider of comprehensive and comprehensive IT and telecommunication solutions and services to all customers around the world. With our ethical, professional and innovative approach, we create a meaningful working environment for our employees, bringing to customers innovative values ​​and excellent service, aiming to raise prices. Equal to shareholders and accountable to the community.</p>\n<p>Mobi Plus has made great progress since its inception. The annual growth rate of sauluon is higher than previous years and the number of employees increases c