("754","1","2018-09-17 20:35:54","2018-09-17 13:35:54","[ux_banner height=\"198px\" bg=\"269\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.31)\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"40\" width__sm=\"60\" position_x=\"0\" position_y=\"50\" text_align=\"left\"]\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 65%;\">About us</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/about-us/?lang=en\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"#\">About us</a> &gt; General Introduce</p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[section label=\"Section gioi thieu\" class=\"section-gioi-thieu\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\" class=\"cot1\"]\n\n[title text=\"ABOUT MOBIPLUS\"]\n\n<div class=\"menu-gioi-thieu-chung\">\n<p><a href=\"/general-introduction/?lang=en\">General Intruduce</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/our-partners/?lang=en\">Our Partner</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/customer/?lang=en\">Our Customer</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/social-activities/?lang=en\">Social Activities</a></p>\n</div>\n[gap height=\"20px\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tieu-de\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600; font-size: 95%;\">NEWS - RECRUITMENT</span></h3>\n[blog_posts style=\"vertical\" type=\"row\" col_spacing=\"small\" columns=\"1\" columns__md=\"1\" cat=\"3\" posts=\"4\" show_date=\"false\" excerpt=\"false\" comments=\"false\" image_height=\"89%\" image_width=\"25\" text_pos=\"middle\" text_align=\"left\" text_size=\"small\"]\n\n[contact-form-7 id=\"799\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>Mobi Plus is a provider of comprehensive and comprehensive IT and telecommunication solutions and services to all customers around the world. With our ethical, professional and innovative approach, we create a meaningful working environment for our employees, bringing to customers innovative values ​​and excellent service, aiming to raise prices. Equal to shareholders and accountable to the community.</p>\n<p>Mobi Plus has made great progress since its inception. The annual growth rate of sauluon is higher than previous years and the number of employees increases continuously every year. Currently, Mobi Plus has member companies in countries such as the US, Singapore and a diverse customer base globally. With the strategy of \"bringing global knowledge into Vietnam and bringing Vietnam\'s resources to the global market\" - Mobi Plus wishes to become a leading company in Vietnam and the region. Quality of service and efficiency in activities on the basis of IT knowledge.</p>\n<p>In the global market, Mobi Plus is one of the first companies in Vietnam operating in software outsourcing since 2007, our software engineer team has been certified by Carnegie Mellon on a daily basis. \"Rope Effectiveness\" for many large customers across the world by A3 formula * C3 = ROO.<br />\nIn Vietnam market, Mobi Plus now offers solutions for e-government and integrated solutions for enterprises and organizations. Most of the key ministries, as well as major financial institutions and companies in Vietnam are already customers of Mobi Plus. Mobi Plus is also the leader in implementing the PPP model to promote the effectiveness and quality of social infrastructure services such as education, culture and health based on IT knowledge.</p>\n[row_inner style=\"small\"]\n\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"342\" img_width=\"600\" pos=\"center\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Mobi Plus wishes to become a strong, constantly innovating, innovative company with a global vision of corporate action, but with a compact, flexible and dynamic structure as a small company. , contribute to build the country, bring life to prosperity for all members.</p>\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"344\" img_width=\"600\" pos=\"center\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our mission is to support organizations, businesses who are aware of their potential, and raise customers to a new level of technology-based innovation. All our actions are directed towards this mission.</p>\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"343\" img_width=\"600\" pos=\"center\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Be honest, open-minded, respectful of customers, colleagues? passionate about technology; Responsible for customers, shareholders, partners, colleagues and society; take initiative, seek, create, accept every challenge to pass; Always self-critical, perfect yourself and employ talent.</p>\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]","About us","","publish","closed","closed","","about-us","","","2018-10-08 16:38:12","2018-10-08 09:38:12","","0","https://tppone.com/demo/mobiplus/?page_id=754&#038;lang=en","0","page","","0"),
